(35, '4', 'SELECTED TOPICS/COMPUTER SCI: ST/ ADVANCED WEB DEVELOPMENT', 'CS 419', 0, 'Topics of special and current interest not covered in other courses.', 'Enrollment limited to students in the College of Engineering college.'),
