(299, '3', 'INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY IN AGRICULTURE', 'AG 111', 0, 'Using information technology in agriculture and agribusiness; practical experience with computer programs applicable to all agricultural disciplines.', 'Enrollment is limited to students with a program in General Agriculture (140) or Agricultural Sciences (259).'),
