(729, '2', 'SPECIAL TOPICS: Speculating Futures', 'ART 399H', 0, '', 'Enrollment limited to students in a Honors Bachelor of Arts, Honors Bachelor of Fine Arts or Honors Bachelor of Science degrees.Enrollment limited to students in the Oregon State - Cascades campus.'),
