(832, '2', 'SEMINAR: SEM/ LEARN TO LOVE LYING EYES', 'BB 407H', 0, 'Informal seminars presenting information about research problems and careers and research programs on campus in biochemistry or biophysics.', 'Enrollment limited to students in a Honors Bachelor of Arts, Honors Bachelor of Fine Arts or Honors Bachelor of Science degrees.'),
(833, '2', 'SEMINAR: SEMINAR/ PROTEIN PORTRAITS', 'BB 407H', 0, 'Informal seminars presenting information about research problems and careers and research programs on campus in biochemistry or biophysics.', 'Enrollment limited to students in a Honors Bachelor of Arts, Honors Bachelor of Fine Arts or Honors Bachelor of Science degrees.'),
