(1062, '1 to 6', 'PROJECTS: CURATORIAL ASSISTANT', 'BOT 406', 0, 'Students assist with curatorial projects in the OSU Herbarium. Admission is by application to the Department of Botany &amp; Plant Pathology.', '');
