(1323, '3', 'FND SKILLS FOR GEN CHEM', 'CH 101', 0, 'Provides some extra preparation for students before enrolling in a general chemistry course. Emphasizes the skills required to be successful in general chemistry and the use of those skill in the context of chemistry concepts.', 'Prerequisites: minimum score of 046 in \'Math Placement - ALEKS\', MTH 095*, 103*, 111, 241, 251, 251H, 252 or 252H.* May be taken concurrently.A minimum grade of C- is required in MTH 095, MTH 103, MTH 111, MTH 241, MTH 251, MTH 251H, MTH 252 and MTH 252H.'),
