(1903, '3', '^SUPPORTIVE DIFFERENTIATED ENVIRONMENTS', 'ED 340', 0, 'Addresses special abilities and needs of learners and helps prepare teachers to develop strategies and instructional practices for diverse learners and students with exceptionalities in a supportive and inclusive classroom. (Writing Intensive Course)', 'Enrollment is limited to students with a program in Education (233).'),
