(2145, '3', 'RADIO FREQUENCY IC DESIGN', 'ECE 621', 2, 'Radio frequency (RF) circuits. Principles, analysis, and design of bipolar and MOS RF IC building blocks: low noise amplifiers, mixers, oscillators, frequency synthesizers.', 'Enrollment is limited to Graduate level students.Enrollment limited to students in the College of Engineering college.'),
