(2175, '3', '*CREATIVE COLLABORATION: DESIGNING AND BUILDING', 'ENGR 352', 0, 'Working in multi-disciplinary teams, design, implement, and document a piece of public art work or science museum display. Projects may be made of any media, but must demonstrate creativity both in the engineering used to create them and the technology and society message they convey. CROSSLISTED as ART 352/ENGR 352. (Bacc Core Course)', ''),
