(2291, '4', '*^PERSPECTIVES IN ENVIRONMENTAL ARTS AND HUMANITIES', 'EAH 411', 0, 'Introduction to methods of inquiry in the field of environmental arts and humanities. Students will learn key concepts in approaches to environmental humanities scholarship and environmental art, informed by ecological principles and other perspectives from the natural sciences. Disciplinary approaches include history, literature, philosophy, and the formal arts. (Bacc Core Course) (Writing Intensive Course)', ''),
