(2328, '4', 'GROUNDWATER REMEDIATION', 'ENVE 554', 2, 'Theory and practice of groundwater remediation. Environmental site assessments. Physical, chemical, and biological methods for in situ treatment of contaminated aquifers. Modeling of remediation technologies.', ''),
