(2393, '4', 'RACISM AND THE PRISON INDUSTRIAL COMPLEX', 'ES 561', 2, 'The prison industrial/punishment complex in the late 20th and early 21st centuries has become a growth industry with the privatization of prisons, and mass incarceration of mostly people-of-color. This course examines the history and growth of this industry and the implications that it has on this democracy.', ''),
