(2524, '3', 'PROJECTS', 'FW 506', 2, 'Projects are synthesis papers or outreach products that are developed with a mentor from campus, a natural resource agency, or the student\'s place of employment. The purpose of your project is to contribute to the field of study with a product that reflects the principles and applications learned in your classes.', ''),
