(2706, '3', 'MARKET TOOLS FOR MANAGING GREENHOUSE GAS EMISSIONS', 'FES 500', 2, 'Examines the use of market-based approaches to managing greenhouse gas emissions; the role of forestry and natural resource management in mitigating greenhouse gas emissions; and the design of carbon and offset markets in the context of broader climate change policies. CROSSLISTED as FES 500/MNR 500.', ''),
