(3051, '3', 'SELECTED TOPICS IN GERMAN LANGUAGE', 'GER 319', 0, 'Focus on development of German language skills and/or history of the language. Conducted in German. May be repeated for credit when topic varies. Lec/rec. Not offered every year.', ''),
