(3419, '1 to 16', 'THESIS', 'HORT 403', 0, '', 'Enrollment is limited to students with a program in Horticulture (145).'),
(3420, '1', 'PROJECTS: DATA PRESENTATIONS', 'HORT 406', 0, 'For any student doing research, to learn to develop and evaluate poster and slide presentations containing scientific data. Students are exposed to a variety of scientific disciplines as they prepare and critique their own and other students\' posters and oral presentations. Students improve written and oral communication skills. Letter grade is based on participation, improvement, and the quality of a final poster project and oral presentation. Offered winter term. CROSSLISTED as BRR 406/HORT 406.', ''),
(3421, '1', 'SEMINAR', 'HORT 407', 0, 'Senior seminar intended to instruct students on proper techniques for presentation of scientific material. Each student is expected to prepare and present a scientific seminar and to attend and evaluate the seminars given by other class members.', 'Enrollment limited to students with a term level of Senior.Enrollment is limited to students with a program in Crop and Soil Science (120) or Horticulture (145).'),
