(3525, '4', 'APPLIED QUANTITATIVE METHODS I: ANOVA', 'HDFS 531', 2, 'Principles and application of general linear models for categorical predictors and repeated measures designs (e.g., ANOVA).', 'Prerequisite: HDFS 529.A minimum grade of B- is required in HDFS 529.Enrollment is limited to Graduate level students.'),
(3526, '4', 'APPLIED QUANTITATIVE METHODS II: LINEAR REGRESSION', 'HDFS 532', 2, 'Principles and application of general linear models for continuous predictors (e.g., multiple regression).', 'Prerequisite: HDFS 531.A minimum grade of B- is required in HDFS 531.Enrollment limited to students in the College of Health & Human Sci or Public Health & Human Sci colleges.'),
