(4274, '3', 'MICROBIAL SYSTEMS', 'MB 513', 2, 'Presentation of a modern view of microbiology through the lens of microbes\' influences on our planet\'s habitats and inhabitants. Discusses current research and the use of advanced techniques to illustrate how microbiology is contributing to many cross-disciplinary problems that can involve engineering, public health, sociology, ecology, geology, etc.', ''),
