(5128, '1', 'CONDITIONING', 'PAC 130', 0, 'Total body approach to fitness, cardiorespiratory conditioning, muscular strength and endurance; flexibility emphasized. May follow a specific training format, e.g., ROTC section follows Army conditioning format.', 'Enrollment limited to students in the Oregon State - Cascades campus.'),
