(5283, '1', 'INTERDISCIPLINARY YOGA', 'PAC 293H', 0, 'Basic yoga poses (asanas) using specific techniques and sequences to promote flexibility, strength, relaxation, and a sense of well-being will be used. Integrative concepts between yoga and our daily life will be examined as well as yoga in relationship to other forms of physical movement.', 'Enrollment limited to students in a Honors Bachelor of Arts, Honors Bachelor of Fine Arts or Honors Bachelor of Science degrees.'),
(5284, '1', 'INTERDISCIPLINARY YOGA: INTERDIS YOGA/ MINDFULNESS', 'PAC 293H', 0, 'Basic yoga poses (asanas) using specific techniques and sequences to promote flexibility, strength, relaxation, and a sense of well-being will be used. Integrative concepts between yoga and our daily life will be examined as well as yoga in relationship to other forms of physical movement.', 'Enrollment limited to students in a Honors Bachelor of Arts, Honors Bachelor of Fine Arts or Honors Bachelor of Science degrees.'),
(5285, '1', 'YOGA I', 'PAC 294', 0, 'Principles and practice of basic yoga postures, techniques of posture alignment, yogi breathing styles and their impact on the body and mind. Students will be exposed to a variety of forms of yoga, as well as basic yoga philosophy.', ''),
