(5358, '3', 'CAPSTONES IN PHYSICS: THERMAL AND STATISTICAL PHYSICS', 'PH 441', 0, 'Entropy and quantum mechanics; canonical Gibbs probability; ideal gas; thermal radiation; Einstein and Debye lattices; grand canonical Gibbs probability; ideal Fermi and Bose gases; chemical reactions and phase transformations.', ''),
