(5564, '1', 'ETHICS IN PSYCHOLOGICAL RESEARCH', 'PSY 523', 2, 'Covers research ethics in psychology. Topics include the history of research-oriented ethical guidelines, ethical principles, working with an IRB, questionable research practices, and fraud. Meets OSU?s Learning Outcome regarding the ethical conduct of research.', 'Enrollment is limited to students with a major in Psychology (9700).Enrollment is limited to Graduate level students.'),
