(5567, '4', 'LIFESPAN DEVELOPMENTAL SCIENCE', 'PSY 551', 2, 'The study of human change and stability over time. Topics may include, but are not limited to, theories, methodological approaches, and contexts for development, social development, cognitive development, and biopsychosocial processes including temperament and personality, resilience, health, thriving, emotion regulation, and developmental contexts.', 'Enrollment is limited to Graduate level students.'),
