(5626, '2', 'SEMINAR: IS/ PRE-INTERNSHIP', 'H 407', 0, 'Seminar to prepare students for their internship in public health. Focus is on professionalism, leadership skills, identifying strengths, and transitioning from college to graduate school or the working world.', 'Students with a term level of Freshman or Sophomore may not enroll.Enrollment is limited to students with a program in Public Health (239), Environmental Safety & Health (704) or Environmental & Occupat Health (747).'),
(5627, '2', 'SEMINAR: SEM: IS/PRE-INTERNSHIP', 'H 407', 0, 'Seminar to prepare students for their internship in public health. Focus is on professionalism, leadership skills, identifying strengths, and transitioning from college to graduate school or the working world.', 'Students with a term level of Freshman or Sophomore may not enroll.Enrollment is limited to students with a program in Public Health (239), Environmental Safety & Health (704) or Environmental & Occupat Health (747).'),
