(6106, '3', 'HISPAN STUDIES: HISP STUDY CTR: MODERN LATIN AMERICAN LIT', 'SPAN 488', 0, 'Section 1: Topics, Hispanic language. Section 2: Practical work (exercises). Section 3: Topics, Hispanic arts and letters. Section 4: Topics, Hispanic society.', ''),
