(6289, '3', 'TARGET ORGAN TOXICOLOGY', 'TOX 512', 2, 'Examination of toxicological effects of chemicals at organ level. Normal physiology of the organ system is received.', 'Prerequisite: TOX 511.A minimum grade of C is required in TOX 511.'),
