(6747, '4', 'THE TEACHING OF WRITING', 'WR 511', 2, 'Pedagogy and theory in composition; prepares teachers (secondary through college) in writing process, assignment design, evaluation, and grammar. Also focuses on student\'s own writing.', 'Enrollment is limited to students with a major in:History of Science (5440)Women, Gender, and Sexuality (8008)Environmental Arts & Humanitie (8200)Women Studies (8680)English (8900)Creative Writing (8920)Applied Ethics (9580)Interdisciplinary Studies (9900)'),
