(6794, '4', 'CONCEPTS IN DIGITAL IMAGING', 'ART 348', 0, 'Approaches to non-traditional and the manipulated image in digital photography with an emphasis on producing personal imagery. Introduction to the history of the manipulated image in photography and to contemporary approaches to digital photography.', 'Prerequisite: ART 263.A minimum grade of D- is required in ART 263.'),
